item.title: About
item.description: I mostly blog about intuition and concepts in AI and Machine Learning and subjects associated with them (statistics, programming etc.). I am on a journey to explore these topics. I find them fascinating. I take notes as I read, listen, learn. These blog posts are extensions of my notes. These are mostly for me to read later. You may find them helpful as well. I am this person.
